hopobject.body: I'm interested in hcahealthcare.com Still, investors are calm as Patrick Armstrong of Armstrong Investment Managers explained: “It won’t have a major impact. Where it may have an impact is it may create uncertainty. The longer it does drag on the more impact it will have, because it’ll have consequences on consumers confidence, the unemployment rate kicks up as you’ve got government workers who aren’t employed. And it’ll probably create a bit more uncertainty about the budget crisis that’s looming at the middle of this month as well, so the longer it drags on, it potentially may become more material.”
